channel.title: Starscape | Need Testers | IN BETA
channel.description:
Hello Moparscape forumers. My partner Ethan and I are looking to create a one-of-a-kind server that will feature a few different things from classic servers. We plan to take this server places and we would like to be able to provide a secure, happy, and fun experience for all players.
[b]What positions are available?[/b] [u]Coder[/u] [3/3] [u]Web Developer/Webmaster[/u] [1/1] [u]Host[/u] [1/1]
[b]Goals[/b]
[ul][li]Stable economy[/li] [li]Active community[/li] [li]Self-sufficient server[/li] [li]Unique features[/li] [li]24/7 VPS[/li] [li]vBulletin forums[/li][/ul]

item.title: Starscape | Need Testers | IN BETA
item.dc:creator: @Pull_Ups Pull Ups
item.description:
@Pull_Ups wrote:

We’re not trying to make an extremely common server. We are starting with a barely coded base with the basics coded already. Alfansor has begun fixing up the mess that the base coder created… Once we are done with that we plan to create new parts to the server such as PKBox and FunPK. We will do our best the keep all of our updates 100% working. Remember that we are both learning as we go. We plan to have as much fun with this server as possible.

OT: I have lowered the age requirement to 14.
